citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately
11:30 am on 02/29/2016.
The inspectors spoke with the licensee and the licensee stated that they had to leave for an appointment. The
inspectors let the licensee know that an attempted inspection would be written.
Additional Inspectors
Moore Chad, Animal Care Inspector
